vely, the lack of clouds in 2MASS J21392676+0220226\nwould also explain the lack of polarization. Further linear polarimetric\nmonitoring of 2MASS J21392676+0220226, during at least one full rotational\nperiod, would help to confirm or discard the existence of clouds in its\natmosphere.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Mar 2023 18:58:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Mar 2023 16:59:47 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-05"}
