 a range $\\eta\\le\\ell\\ll \\lambda<L$\n\\begin{align}\nS_{3}[\\ell]=\\mathbb{E}\\left[|\\mathcal{U}_{i}(x+\\ell,t)-\\mathcal{U}(x,t)|^{3}\\right]=-\\frac{4}{5}\\epsilon\\ell\\nonumber\n\\end{align} where $\\eta=(\\nu^{3/4}\\epsilon)^{-1/4}$. For the second-order\nstructure function, the 2/3-law emerges as\n$S_{2}[\\ell]=C\\epsilon^{2/3}\\ell^{2/3}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 10 Mar 2023 23:51:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-03-14"}
